column5: Rtmg,Was I right with my original prediction? I said by May 4th. I'mtold it's out now and if not completely it will be in a day orso?
Well, you are right & wrong. Ice is in fact out. Date was April 29.Good FishenRob
Excellent,See you on the water........unfortunately not until the end ofJune.Good Fishing
Ice was out on Pickerel Lake April 28th.
Was wondering if you knew if the ice is out on Black Sturgeon Lake? I'm assuming so, but was curious if you had any first hand info.
